requests.name: Get all feature categories
requests.description: Gets a list of all feature categories used by the BC Geographical Names Information System (BCGNIS).  Note: there are three levels of classification in the BCGNIS feature taxonomy: classes, categories and types.  A type is a subset of a category, and a category is a subset of a class.

queryParams.description: The format of the output.

requests.name: Search for names with metadata changes in a given period

queryParams.description: The format of the output.
Defines the earliest date (YYYY-MM-DD format) of the change time window for the search
Defines the latest date (YYYY-MM-DD format) of the change time window for the search
